snippet.title: Is ‘Bernie or Bust’ A Wise Attitude for Democrats?

localized.description:
Ring of Fire’s Farron Cousins sits down with David Pakman to discuss last week’s New York Primaries, as well as the progression of the ‘Bernie or Bust’ movement. What do you think of "Bernie or Bust?" Let us know in the comments section!
